node.text:
Dolomite Alps In Italy 🇮🇹 are just magical. Some tourists prefer to travel to the Dolomites during the summer, between May and September, when the weather is pleasantly warm and the mountains lively and colorful. Early spring, when crocuses, Alpine snowdrops and scented bushes of Daphne bloom through the melting snow, is equally beautiful.

🎥 @rebe.twosoles 
📍 Dolomites Italy
